node.text:
i am a taurus rising and people usually mistake me for a virgo. i have a virgo moon&mars both trining my asc. but my asc also conjuncts my taurus saturn and squares my aquarius uranus.

what about you? 🤑

want to know how to find your aspects? read below + keep swiping!

here are three ways out of a dozen+!

1) second image; not my chart. website is astrotheme.com. i have a link + tutorial on my highlights (“birth chart tutorial”). calculate your chart, click the checkboxes, click redraw. scroll down to the “list of aspects” as boxed in the example picture. anything that mentions “AS” means it’s aspecting your ascendant! if there is nothing, that means nothing aspects your asc.

2. third and fourth images; not my chart. website is astro-charts.com. calculate your chart, scroll down to where it says “aspects” and find everything that mentions “ascendant.” those are the aspects to your ascendant! if there is nothing, that means nothing aspects your asc.

3. fifth image. download an app like “time passages”, enter in your info to get your chart calculated, find “my chart”, find “aspects” and find anything that mentions your ascendant! however it won’t mention all of your aspects like the websites will. time passages only shows one aspect to my ascendant when i have more than just one!

#realastrologies #realastrologytwt #realastrologyrising #realastrologyasc
